{"tid":103691,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人試過耳仔好似有野塞住左?","createTime":"2017-02-01T13:52:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-16T10:06:39.000Z","uid":39150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"037c39cc88fc215b2ab357b3c81ac4ec0ae9ea12","tid":103691,"uid":39150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T13:52:02.000Z","msg":"我隻右耳無啦啦好似有層膜塞住左咁<br />\n左耳又乜事都無喎...<br />\n明明細個都無....<br />\n係上年先開始...滴左幾滴耳油幾日就無事<br />\n上2個禮拜又黎...<br />\n已經塞左2個星期啦...會唔會失聰架?<br />\n<br />\np.s有無人試過分享下"},{"pid":"61a21c3027f3c215d57b706255e1019b54f6b5cc","tid":103691,"uid":60136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T13:56:52.000Z","msg":"因為個耳管道形狀生得不利耳屎自然排出 左耳試過比耳屎塞左<br />\n<br />\n最後要去睇耳鼻喉科等醫生清"},{"pid":"6635650073246f6a9b6d8e43802257ad7f6ae186","tid":103691,"uid":25052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T13:56:57.000Z","msg":"我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我係左耳<br />\n前排滴完耳油仲以為通番哂<br />\n但點知今朝一起身就發覺塞住左<br />\n今日放工諗住睇醫生但屋企附近啲診所仲放緊假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5809ff94203483c1c13fae3db31e840411b11e8a","tid":103691,"uid":31752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T14:01:13.000Z","msg":"因為真係塞住囉<br />\n入水耳屎脹大就塞架啦<br />\n<br />\n去藥房買支大針筒<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.medtronic.com/content/dam/covidien/library/global/en/product/needles-and-syringes/monoject-140ml-piston-syringes-f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.medtronic.com%2Fcontent%2Fdam%2Fcovidien%2Flibrary%2Fglobal%2Fen%2Fproduct%2Fneedles-and-syringes%2Fmonoject-140ml-piston-syringes-f.jpg&h=767db659&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n對住隻耳慢慢射(唔洗大力)<br />\n射5分鐘就清返出黎<br />\n<br />\n診所都係咁洗"},{"pid":"1318856a14bd6d5acac9ba449c817e7d6eb9d17d","tid":103691,"uid":39150,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T14:02:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為真係塞住囉<br />\n入水耳屎脹大就塞架啦<br />\n<br />\n去藥房買支大針筒<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.medtronic.com/content/dam/covidien/library/global/en/product/needles-and-syringes/monoject-140ml-piston-syringes-f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.medtronic.com%2Fcontent%2Fdam%2Fcovidien%2Flibrary%2Fglobal%2Fen%2Fproduct%2Fneedles-and-syringes%2Fmonoject-140ml-piston-syringes-f.jpg&h=767db659&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n對住隻耳慢慢射(唔洗大力)<br />\n射5分鐘就清返出黎<br />\n<br />\n診所都係咁洗</blockquote><br />\n巴打你自己通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49dd7261524b280a3f7e105401ee476810151657","tid":103691,"uid":39150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T14:03:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為個耳管道形狀生得不利耳屎自然排出 左耳試過比耳屎塞左<br />\n<br />\n最後要去睇耳鼻喉科等醫生清</blockquote><br />\n你睇左幾錢阿?<br />\n我問過專科要成千5蚊"},{"pid":"b574f7b81277a9132c0d75c705ea2198605da683","tid":103691,"uid":31752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T14:05:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為真係塞住囉<br />\n入水耳屎脹大就塞架啦<br />\n<br />\n去藥房買支大針筒<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.medtronic.com/content/dam/covidien/library/global/en/product/needles-and-syringes/monoject-140ml-piston-syringes-f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.medtronic.com%2Fcontent%2Fdam%2Fcovidien%2Flibrary%2Fglobal%2Fen%2Fproduct%2Fneedles-and-syringes%2Fmonoject-140ml-piston-syringes-f.jpg&h=767db659&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n對住隻耳慢慢射(唔洗大力)<br />\n射5分鐘就清返出黎<br />\n<br />\n診所都係咁洗</blockquote><br />\n可以滴啲耳油軟化耳屎先<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/7lt4p2Btvd4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F7lt4p2Btvd4&d=g2%2Fo6b0QjPi1xWtu1PcU8Yzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=61d204e6\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/7lt4p2Btvd4</a>"},{"pid":"b69d912fb87b8a4fe95ef753d2873ca001432306","tid":103691,"uid":20302,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T14:05:58.000Z","msg":"兩星期前撩左耳  冇啦啦塞左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後第二日買左枝洗耳果d 都冇用 <br />\n<br />\n維持左一星期 慢慢冇事聽番清楚<br />\n可能枝野keep住用幫我溶左舊耳屎"},{"pid":"4d54f09b44c805b722d2de91f689dce57522a778","tid":103691,"uid":20302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T14:06:45.000Z","msg":"嚇q死  以後唔用棉花棒撩耳"},{"pid":"a9eab1121ca3d1c90e8016456d937cd3aeab9772","tid":103691,"uid":31752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T14:07:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>因為真係塞住囉<br />\n入水耳屎脹大就塞架啦<br />\n<br />\n去藥房買支大針筒<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.medtronic.com/content/dam/covidien/library/global/en/product/needles-and-syringes/monoject-140ml-piston-syringes-f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.medtronic.com%2Fcontent%2Fdam%2Fcovidien%2Flibrary%2Fglobal%2Fen%2Fproduct%2Fneedles-and-syringes%2Fmonoject-140ml-piston-syringes-f.jpg&h=767db659&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n對住隻耳慢慢射(唔洗大力)<br />\n射5分鐘就清返出黎<br />\n<br />\n診所都係咁洗</blockquote><br />\n巴打你自己通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n試過睇專科拎部專業機通左過千<br />\n後來去診所都係用針筒通<br />\n跟住我就學左自己通<br />\n細細力慢慢射唔危險"},{"pid":"f7395e365628c80e7bcfcebc19c594bd27054e15","tid":103691,"uid":31712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T14:08:44.000Z","msg":"我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 琴晚帶完入耳式耳機打左陣機，今朝就塞左<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2714a9a0705ab7fd03db6f6c34b78174e2e579c","tid":103691,"uid":16772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T14:08:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>因為個耳管道形狀生得不利耳屎自然排出 左耳試過比耳屎塞左<br />\n<br />\n最後要去睇耳鼻喉科等醫生清</blockquote><br />\n你睇左幾錢阿?<br />\n我問過專科要成千5蚊</blockquote><br />\n我都試過比耳屎塞住耳仔  滴過油都冇用<br />\n最後去左通耳  吸番舊耳屎出黎  好大舊  佢仲比番舊屎我留念<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屯門碼頭個耳鼻喉專科醫生舊年都係收1000  可以去睇下"},{"pid"