":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T14:30:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>因為真係塞住囉<br />\n入水耳屎脹大就塞架啦<br />\n<br />\n去藥房買支大針筒<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.medtronic.com/content/dam/covidien/library/global/en/product/needles-and-syringes/monoject-140ml-piston-syringes-f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.medtronic.com%2Fcontent%2Fdam%2Fcovidien%2Flibrary%2Fglobal%2Fen%2Fproduct%2Fneedles-and-syringes%2Fmonoject-140ml-piston-syringes-f.jpg&h=767db659&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n對住隻耳慢慢射(唔洗大力)<br />\n射5分鐘就清返出黎<br />\n<br />\n診所都係咁洗</blockquote><br />\n要放到幾入架?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n對住個窿射入去就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acf8d96e15cf7080169642719a67c1ff1a984128","tid":103691,"uid":33159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T14:32:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>耳油撚 長期塞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都成日塞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  成日要通耳 滴耳藥水都冇用"},{"pid":"6259b8c0bcc706515cf918eaffb6cba84401be24","tid":103691,"uid":16772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T14:32:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n你睇左幾錢阿?<br />\n我問過專科要成千5蚊</blockquote><br />\n我都試過比耳屎塞住耳仔  滴過油都冇用<br />\n最後去左通耳  吸番舊耳屎出黎  好大舊  佢仲比番舊屎我留念<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屯門碼頭個耳鼻喉專科醫生舊年都係收1000  可以去睇下</blockquote><br />\n但係我住港島喎....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁尷尬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e30381f70e205c4cf3a2aa31d75a31d01c4e423","tid":103691,"uid":377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T14:34:52.000Z","msg":"我果時都係比 $500 係寶血醫院耳鼻喉科用針筒沖出黎。"},{"pid":"